<typeStatus>lectotype</typeStatus>
but noted that the type (their f. 12) belongs to 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Peltigeraceae" genus="Peltigera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" phylum="Magnoliophyta" rank="species" species="praetextata">
